penSansRegular, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.6rem;\">What\'s Included: Membership</h4><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding-left: 20px;\"><li>12-month Club membership + 1 Complimentary Membership for someone in your household</li><li>3% cash back on qualifying in-club purchases with Sam’s Club Mastercard®</li><li>Special savings in services like Tire &amp; Battery, Pharmacy and Optical</li><li>Instant Savings throughout the year on already low prices</li><li>**Get 2% back in Sam’s Cash on qualifying purchases in-club (up to $500/year)</li><li><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">Free shipping (exclusions apply)</span></li><li>Free curbside pickup</li><li>Earn 20% more Sam’s Cash in Bonus Offers Program</li></ul><h4 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 5px; font-family: OpenSansRegular, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.6rem;\">Terms &amp; Conditions</h4><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding-left: 20px;\"><li><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">Offer valid for new Sam’s Club Members only</span></li><li><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">Auto-renewal of your Sam’s Club membership is required upon signup.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">Not valid for membership renewals, for those with a current membership, or those who were Sam’s Club members less than 6 months prior to November 1, 2022.</span>.</li><li>To check your renewal date, please check your billing statement or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://gr.pn/2R4oWpR\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 94, 171);\">your online account</a>, or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://help.samsclub.com/app/chat/chat_launch\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 94, 171);\">CHAT with an associate</a>. Please have your membership card or statement on hand.</li><li><a href=\"https://www.groupon.com/pages/n-sams-club-membership-packages-11\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 94, 171);\">See Full Terms</a></li></ul><h4 style=\"margin: 10p