t;1&quot;:95,&quot;2&quot;:{&quot;2&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:1136076},&quot;9&quot;:1}}\" data-sheets-hyperlinkruns=\"{&quot;1&quot;:93,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;https://www.workbenchcon.com/shop/&quot;}{&quot;1&quot;:127}\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">2023 Insider WBCMaker Badge: $549.00<br>2023 Marketing Pass: $979.00<br>2023 WBCMaker Pass: $549.00</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><a class=\"in-cell-link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.workbenchcon.com/shop/\"><br><br></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\"><a class=\"in-cell-link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.workbenchcon.com/shop/\">Tickets On Sale on October 1, 20</a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\">22</span></span></p>', 'https://www.workbenchcon.com/?utm_source=online.marketing', '', '', 549.00, 'yearly', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 07:29:51', '2023-01-17 07:29:51'),
(21, 6, 'DMEXCO - Digital Marketing Exposition & Conference', 'dmexco-digital-marketing-exposition-conference', 'DMEXCO', 'in person', 'uploads/event/63c68bc9065bb23-01-17-11-51-37.jpeg', 'Koelnmesse GmbH Messeplatz 1 50679 Köln  Exhibition Halls 6 - 8 Congress Centre North', NULL, NULL, '50679', NULL, NULL, '2023-09-20', '09:00', '2023-09-21', '17:00', '<p><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;This is what you can look forward to:\\n\\nthe latest trends and technologies at the DMEXCO Expo, including the DMEXCO Worlds and w3.vision, the exclusive Web3 event in the middle of DMEXCO\\nabout 600 top international speakers, 14 stages, 15 summits and more than 200 hours of program at the DMEXCO Conference\\naccess to exclusive partner content, such as whitepapers, downloadables and much more in the DMEXCO app\\nVOD library with all keynotes, panels, lectures and masterclasses after the event\\nYour ticket to DMEXCO 2022 on-site also gives you access to the digital-only wrap-up DMEXCO x Digiday Online on September 27 on the DMEXCO Digital Event Platform\\n\\nPlan Your Visit&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:1049345,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0,&quot;23&quot;:1}\" data-sheets-textstyleruns=\"{&quot;1&quot;:0}{&quot;1&quot;:653,&quot;2&quot;:{&quot;2&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:0}}}{&quot;1&quot;:655,&quot;2&quot;:{&quot;2&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:1136076},&quot;9&quot;:1}}\" data-sheets-hyperlinkruns=\"{&quot;1&quot;:653,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;https://dmexco.com/plan-your-visit/#siteplan-and-opening-hours&quot;}{&quot;1&quot;:668}\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">This is what you can look forward to:<br><br>the latest trends and technologies at the DMEXCO Expo, including the DMEXCO Worlds and w3.vision, the exclusive Web3 event in the middle of DMEXCO<br>about 600 top international speakers, 14 stages, 15 summits and more than 200 hours of program at the DMEXCO Conference<br>access to exclusive partner content, such as whitepapers, downloadables and much more in the DMEXCO app<br>VOD library with all keynotes, panels, lectures and masterclasses after the event<br></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><a class=\"in-cell-link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://dmexco.com/plan-your-visit/#siteplan-and-opening-hours\"><br></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\"><a class=\"in-cell-link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://dmexco.com/plan-your-visit/#siteplan-and-opening-hours\">Plan Your Vis</a></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\">it</span></span></p>', '', '', '', 0.00, '', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 11:51:37', '2023-01-17 11:51:37'),
(22, 5, 'Confab Content Strategy Conference 2023', 'confab-content-strategy-conference-2023', 'Confab', 'in person', 'uploads/event/63c68d0062bcb23-01-17-11-56-48.png', 'Hyatt Regency Minneapolis 1300 Nicollet Mall, Minneapolis, MN 55403', NULL, NULL, '55403', '', NULL, '2023-04-30', '09:00', '2023-05-03', '16:30', '<p><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;Confab is an event for people who care about making content more useful and usable for everyone. And no, you don’t have to be a content strategist to attend! If you lead, design, build, or manage digital content, Confab is where you belong.&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:769,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;11&quot;:4,&quot;12&quot;:0}\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\">Confab is an event for people who care about making content more useful and usable for everyone. And no, you don’t have to be a content strategist to attend! If you lead, design, build, or manage digital content, Confab is where you belong.</span></p>', '', '', '', 2695.00, '', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 11:56:48', '2023-01-17 11:56:48'),
(23, 0, 'THE PPA FESTIVAL', 'the-ppa-festival', 'Professional Publishers Association', '10', 'uploads/event/63c68f74dd4f023-01-17-12-07-16.jpeg', 'THE BREWERY, 52 Chiswell St, London EC1Y 4SA,', NULL, NULL, 'E1W 2SF', 'London', NULL, '2023-04-25', '08:30', '2023-04-25', '17:00', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(48, 55, 63); font-family: Lora; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(233, 226, 219);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">With a new look and new central London location, the PPA is upping the ante on all things Festival. From hard hitting and inspiring content, best-in-class speakers who are defining our industry, to unrivalled networking and learning opportunities.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(48, 55, 63); font-family: Lora; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(233, 226, 219);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Join us on 25 April at The Brewery, where the PPA Festival 2023 will deliver an&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">essential agenda</span>&nbsp;giving you the tools to&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">drive innovation</span>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">deliver success&nbsp;</span>within your business. We</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;will showcase content spanning four stages with focus on People, Product, Audience and Content.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(48, 55, 63); font-family: Lora; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(233, 226, 219);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">The agenda is tailored to all those involved with content, marketing, product, sales, people, creative, data, audience growth, events, audio, web, apps, video, print, and more, from consumer, b2b, small, large, and digital publishing businesses.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Attended by&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">over 500 publishing professionals</span>&nbsp;in consumer and business magazine media, this is the event of the year not to be missed.</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(48, 55, 63); font-family: Lora; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(233, 226, 219);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">What are you waiting for? Tickets are available at the&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Early Bird rate</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;until&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Friday 3 March 2023.</span></span></p>', 'https://ppafestival.co.uk/2023/en/page/home', '', '', 1360.00, '', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 12:07:16', '2023-01-17 12:07:16'),
(24, 0, 'FIFA World Cup 2022', 'fifa-world-cup-2022', 'Global', '15', 'uploads/event/63c690938e4ee23-01-17-12-12-03.png', 'Lusail Iconic Stadium', NULL, NULL, '', 'Doha', 'QA', '2022-11-20', '19:00', '2022-12-18', '18:00', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The biggest sporting event of 2022 will be held in Qatar. It is the first FIFA World Cup to take place in the Middle East and Arab world. The opening match will be played at the Al Bayt Stadium, which was inaugurated in 2021.\r\n\r\nAs in some of the previous editions, 32 football teams will participate in the 2022 FIFA World Cup. France, the defending champions, qualified for the tournament in 2021. Others who qualified by 2021 include Argentina, Brazil, England, Germany and Spain — all of whom are previous FIFA World Cup winners.\r\n\r\nQatar qualified as the host country.</span></p>', 'https://www.fifa.com/fifaplus/en/tournaments/mens/worldcup/qatar2022', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 12:12:03', '2023-01-17 12:12:03'),
(772, 0, 'Australian Open', 'australian-open', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c8f0686525923-01-19-07-25-28.jpeg', 'SC Melbourne Park', NULL, NULL, '', 'Melbourne', 'AU', '2023-01-16', '10:00', '2023-01-29', '16:00', 'Australia Open 2023 is the 108th draw of an international tennis tournament. The championship will be held in the Australian city of Melbourne again, in the territory of the SC Melbourne Park. The main stars of modern tennis – Novak Djokovic, Garbine Muguruza, Roger Federer, Venus Williams- will perform on the courts of the sports complex', 'https://ausopen.club/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-19 07:25:28'),
(773, 0, 'Special Olympics Games Berlin 2023', 'special-olympics-games-berlin-2023', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c69f4cde6b523-01-17-01-14-52.png', 'Friedrich-Friesen-Allee14053 BerlinDistrict Charlottenburg-Wilmersdorf', NULL, NULL, '', 'Charlottenburg-Wilmersdorf', 'DE', '2023-06-17', '', '2023-06-25', '', 'The Special Olympics World Games offer the opportunity to unite the world like no other event can. Here people with and without disabilities, people of different nations, cultures, political views and religions meet and can overcome existing prejudices with the power of sport.\r\n\r\nFrom 17 – 25 June 2023, Berlin, Germany will welcome 7,000 Special Olympics athletes and Unified partners from approximately 170 countries to compete in 24 sports. The athletes will be supported by more than 3,000 coaches and 20,000 volunteers.', 'https://www.berlin2023.org/', '', '', 0.00, 'TBD', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-17 13:14:52'),
(774, 0, 'Summer Olympics 2024', 'summer-olympics-2024', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c6a04d9e7d223-01-17-01-19-09.png', 'Stadiums and Venues around Paris', NULL, NULL, '', 'Paris', 'FR', '2022-07-26', '', '2022-08-12', '', 'With two years to go to the Paris 2024 Olympic Games, the official competition schedule has been released. Check out the full schedule to find out exactly when the world’s greatest athletes will be competing in events such as the 100 m freestyle, the 400 m hurdles, the Olympic marathon, team fencing, as well as the women’s and men’s football, handball and rugby sevens finals.', 'https://www.paris2024.org/', '', '', 0.00, 'every-2-years', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-17 13:19:09'),
(775, 0, 'ICC Women’s Cricket World Cup 2023', 'icc-womens-cricket-world-cup-2023', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c6a0c35e64123-01-17-01-21-07.png', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Cape Town', 'AF', '2023-10-02', '', '2023-02-26', '', 'The eighth edition of the ICC Women\'s T20 World Cup will begin on 10 February 2023 with hosts South Africa taking on Sri Lanka. Cape Town, Paarl and Gqeberha will host the matches in the tournament with the knockout matches set to be played in Cape Town.\r\n\r\nThe final will be held on 26 February 2023 with a reserve day available on the 27th in case of major interruptions in play on the designated date.', 'https://www.icc-cricket.com/homepage', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-17 13:21:07'),
(776, 0, '2023 United Nations Security Council Election', '2023-united-nations-security-council-election', '', '16', 'uploads/event/63c6a174d353023-01-17-01-24-04.png', 'United Nations Headquarters', NULL, NULL, '', 'New York', 'US', '', '', '', '', 'The 2023 United Nations Security Council election will be held in mid-2023 during the 77th session of the United Nations General Assembly, held at United Nations Headquarters in New York City. The elections are for five non-permanent seats on the UN Security Council for two-year mandates commencing on 1 January 2024. In accordance with the Security Council\'s rotation rules, whereby the ten non-permanent UNSC seats rotate among the various regional blocs into which UN member states traditionally divide themselves for voting and representation purposes, the five available seats are allocated as follows:', 'https://news.un.org/en/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-17 13:25:53'),
(777, 0, 'French Open 2023', 'french-open-2023', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c6a1d38058a23-01-17-01-25-39.png', 'Roland Garros Stadium', NULL, NULL, '', 'Paris', 'FR', '2023-05-28', '11:00', '2023-06-11', '15:00', 'The best in tennis come together to battle it out for the world’s greatest clay court championship, the 2023 French Open!\r\n\r\nHeld at the famous Roland Garros Stadium in Paris, France, the second tournament of the Grand Slam is the only one to be played on a clay court. Considered by many to be a much more difficult surface to play on than grass (due to the slower moving, yet higher bouncing ball), this court and tournament force players to demonstrate their true skill, and prove that they have what it takes to walk away with the Grand Slam title.', 'https://www.rolandgarros.com/en-us/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-17 13:25:39'),
(778, 0, '2023 Wimbledon Championships', '2023-wimbledon-championships', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c6a22d4aaa723-01-17-01-27-09.png', 'All England Lawn Tennis & Croquet ClubChurch Rd, London SW19 5AG, United Kingdom', NULL, NULL, '', 'London', 'UK', '2023-07-03', '', '2023-07-16', '', 'The most prestigious tennis tournament, Wimbledon, makes a return for 2023!\r\nThis is an occasion where the greatest players in the world get together to compete to win the biggest prize of them all. This is a spectacle not to miss for the eager fans sitting in the stands and grandstands of the infamous Centre Court.', 'https://www.wimbledon.com/en_GB/atoz/dates.html', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-17 13:27:09'),
(779, 0, 'Commonwealth Games 2026', 'commonwealth-games-2026', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c6a299c552b23-01-17-01-28-57.png', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Victoria', 'AU', '2026-03-17', '', '2026-03-29', '', 'At Victoria 2026, sport is just the beginning.\r\nThe 2026 Commonwealth Games will include a keen focus on ensuring works benefit Victoria long after the Games have concluded.\r\nAthlete villages in all four regional hubs will become social and affordable housing, to help regional communities grow and thrive.\r\nNew and upgraded sports infrastructure which will help make regional Victoria the ideal place for major events, providing world-class facilities for local sporting clubs and the packed calendar of sport and events which Victoria attracts.\r\nBeyond infrastructure, Victoria 2026 will help reinforce Victoria’s commitment to diversity and inclusion, while significantly strengthening international relationships throughout the Commonwealth through sport diplomacy.\r\nVictoria 2026 is also committed to providing a platform that recognises Australian Aboriginal history and culture.\r\nVictoria 2026 will showcase everything regional Victoria has to offer to the world – the best food and wine, outstanding arts and culture, and breathtaking landscapes.', 'https://thecgf.com/games/victoria-2026', '', '', 0.00, 'every-4-years', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-17 13:28:57'),
(780, 0, 'US Open [Tennis]', 'us-open-tennis', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c6a3071fd4723-01-17-01-30-47.png', 'Los Angeles Country Club', NULL, NULL, '', 'Los Angeles', 'US', '2023-06-15', '', '2023-06-18', '', 'The US Open will be in 2023 in Los Angeles California.', 'https://www.usopen.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-17 13:30:47'),
(781, 0, 'Hangzhou 2022 Asian Games', 'hangzhou-2022-asian-games', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c6a389d9eaa23-01-17-01-32-57.png', 'Hangzhou Olympic Sports Expo Center', NULL, NULL, '', 'Hangzhou', 'CH', '2023-09-23', '', '2023-10-08', '', 'The 2022 Asian Games, officially known as the 19th Asian Games and also known as Hangzhou 2022, will be a multi-sport event celebrated in Hangzhou, Zhejiang, China. Hangzhou will be the third Chinese city to host the Asian Games, after Beijing in 1990 and Guangzhou in 2010.', 'https://www.hangzhou2022.cn/En/', '', '', 0.00, 'every-4-years', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-17 13:32:57'),
(782, 0, 'SuperBowl 2023', 'superbowl-2023', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c6a4c15073623-01-17-01-38-09.jpeg', 'State Farm Stadium', NULL, NULL, '', 'Arizona', 'US', '2023-02-12', '19:00', '2023-02-12', '', 'The game is scheduled to be played on February 12, 2023, at State Farm Stadium in Glendale, Arizona. It was announced in September, that international popstar, entrepreneur, and philanthropist Rihanna will headline the halftime show at Super Bowl 202', 'https://www.nbcsports.com/washington/commanders/super-bowl-locations-2023-2024-and-beyond', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-17 13:38:09'),
(783, 0, 'U.S. Gymnastics Championships', 'us-gymnastics-championships', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c6a52befca023-01-17-01-39-55.png', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'TBA', 'US', '2023-08-24', '', '2023-08-28', '', 'This event is a 4-day competition involving the top gymnasts in the US in the junior and senior level for men and women artistic gymnastics.', 'https://usagym.org/pages/index.html', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-17 13:39:55'),
(784, 0, 'FA Cup Final 2023', 'fa-cup-final-2023', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c6a5982a38423-01-17-01-41-44.jpeg', 'Wembley Stadium', NULL, NULL, '', 'London', 'UK', '2023-06-03', '', '2023-06-03', '', 'the FA Cup is a knockout competition for virtually all football clubs in England, as well as a few in Wales. It begins in August with fully amateur clubs, and with each ensuing round, larger clubs enter the competition, always via random draw to determine who plays at home and who plays away. The Final at Wembley Stadium is usually in May but this year is in June.', 'https://www.thefa.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-17 13:41:44'),
(785, 0, 'Stanley Cup Finals (Ice Hockey)', 'stanley-cup-finals-ice-hockey', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c6a665377fd23-01-17-01-45-09.webp', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'TBA', 'TBA', '', '', '', '', 'The Stanley Cup is a trophy awarded annually to the playoff champion club of the National Hockey League (NHL) ice hockey league. It was donated by the Governor General of Canada Lord Stanley of Preston in 1892, and is the oldest professional sports trophy in North America.', 'https://www.nhl.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-17 13:45:09'),
(786, 0, 'UEFA Championship (Football/Soccer)', 'uefa-championship-footballsoccer', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c6a6d73e49823-01-17-01-47-03.jpeg', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'TBA', 'TBA', '2023-06-27', '', '', '', 'The UEFA Champions League is an annual club football competition organised by the Union of European Football Associations and contested by top-division European clubs, deciding the competition winners through a round robin group stage to qualify for a double-legged knockout format, and a single leg final.', 'https://www.uefa.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-17 13:47:03'),
(787, 0, '2023 Tour de France', '2023-tour-de-france', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c6a984b530723-01-17-01-58-28.webp', '', NULL, NULL, '', 'Basque Country', 'FR', '2023-07-01', '', '2023-07-23', '', 'The Tour de France is an annual men\'s multiple-stage bicycle race primarily held in France, while also occasionally passing through nearby countries. Like the other Grand Tours, it consists of 21 stages, each a day long, over the course of 23 days, coinciding with the Bastille Day holiday.', 'https://www.letour.fr/en/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-17 13:58:28'),
(788, 0, 'Grand Final (AFL)', 'grand-final-afl', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c6ab45a1bb623-01-17-02-05-57.jpeg', 'Melbourne Cricket Ground', NULL, NULL, '', 'Melbourne', 'AU', '2023-09-23', '', '2023-09-23', '', 'The Australian Football League is the pre-eminent and only fully professional competition of Australian rules football. Through the AFL Commission, the AFL also serves as the sport\'s governing body and is responsible for controlling the laws of the game.', 'https://www.afl.com.au/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-17 14:05:57'),
(789, 0, 'NRL Grand Final (Rugby)', 'nrl-grand-final-rugby', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c78a0436c3823-01-18-05-56-20.webp', 'Accor Stadium', NULL, NULL, '', 'Sydney', 'AU', '2023-10-01', '', '2023-10-01', '', 'The NRL is the pre-eminent rugby league club competition in Australia and New Zealand. It contains clubs from the original New South Wales Rugby League premiership, which had been running continuously since 1908. Teams from Queensland, Victoria, the Australian Capital Territory and New Zealand also play in the league.', 'https://www.nrl.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 05:56:20'),
(790, 0, 'World Series (Baseball)', 'world-series-baseball', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c78a520e97023-01-18-05-57-38.jpeg', 'LoanDepot Park', NULL, NULL, '', 'Miami Florida', 'US', '2023-03-21', '', '2023-03-21', '', 'The World Series is the annual championship series of Major League Baseball in the United States and Canada, contested since 1903 between the champion teams of the American League and the National League.', 'https://www.mlb.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 05:57:38'),
(791, 0, 'US Masters Tournament PGA Tour', 'us-masters-tournament-pga-tour', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c78a949bb1723-01-18-05-58-44.png', 'Augusta National Golf Course', NULL, NULL, '', 'Georgia', 'US', '2023-04-06', '', '2023-04-09', '', 'The 2023 Masters Tournament will be the 87th time this tournament is played. The Masters Tournament was first played in 1934, co-founded by Bobby Jones in Augusta, Georgia. It is one of the four major championships of men\'s professional golf.', 'https://www.masters.com/en_US/index.html', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 05:58:44'),
(792, 0, 'US PGA 2023', 'us-pga-2023', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c78ae3c76f823-01-18-06-00-03.webp', 'Oklahoma\'s Southern Hills Country Club', NULL, NULL, '', 'Oak Hills, New York', 'US', '2023-05-18', '', '2023-05-21', '', 'The PGA Championship is an annual golf tournament conducted by the Professional Golfers\' Association of America. It is one of the four men\'s major championships in professional golf.', 'https://www.pgachampionship.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 06:00:03'),
(793, 0, 'US Open 2023', 'us-open-2023', '', '15', NULL, 'Los Angeles Country Club', NULL, NULL, '', 'Los Angeles, CA', 'US', '2023-06-15', '', '2023-06-18', '', 'The United States Open Championship, commonly known as the U.S. Open, is the annual open national championship of golf in the United States. It is the third of the four major championships in golf, and is on the official schedule of both the PGA Tour and the European Tour.', 'https://www.usopen.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 06:01:21'),
(794, 0, 'British Open 2023', 'british-open-2023', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c78b97a3b1823-01-18-06-03-03.webp', 'Royal Liverpool Golf Course', NULL, NULL, '', 'Wirral CH47 4AL', 'UK', '2023-07-20', '', '2023-07-23', '', 'The Open Championship, often referred to as The Open or the British Open, is the oldest golf tournament in the world, and one of the most prestigious. Founded in 1860, it was originally held annually at Prestwick Golf Club in Scotland.', 'https://www.theopen.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 06:03:03'),
(795, 0, 'Daytona 500', 'daytona-500', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c78c0c3ae5823-01-18-06-05-00.jpeg', 'Daytona International Speedway', NULL, NULL, '', 'Daytona Beach, Florida', 'US', '2023-02-19', '', '2023-11-11', '', 'The Daytona 500 is a 500-mile-long NASCAR Cup Series motor race held annually at Daytona International Speedway in Daytona Beach, Florida.', 'https://www.daytonainternationalspeedway.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 06:05:00'),
(796, 0, '2023 Formula One World Championship', '2023-formula-one-world-championship', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c78c7644fa123-01-18-06-06-46.jpeg', 'Worldwide', NULL, NULL, '', 'Worldwide', 'Worldwide', '2023-03-05', '', '2023-11-26', '', 'The 2023 FIA Formula One World Championship is a planned motor racing championship for Formula One cars which will be the 74th running of the Formula One World Championship.[a] It is recognised by the Fédération Internationale de l\'Automobile (FIA), the governing body of international motorsport, as the highest class of competition for open-wheel racing cars. The championship is due to be contested over a record twenty-four Grands Prix, which will be held around the world, and it is scheduled to begin in March and to end in November.', 'https://www.formula1.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 06:06:46'),
(797, 0, '28th Annual Critics Choice Awards', '28th-annual-critics-choice-awards', '', '20', 'uploads/event/63c8f38b00ae023-01-19-07-38-51.jpeg', 'Fairmont Century Plaza Hotel', NULL, NULL, '', 'Los Angeles, CA', 'US', '2023-01-15', '', '2023-01-15', '', 'The Critics\' Choice Movie Awards (formerly known as the Broadcast Film Critics Association Award) is an awards show presented annually by the American-Canadian Critics Choice Association (CCA) to honor the finest in cinematic achievement.', 'https://www.criticschoice.com/', '', '', 0.00, '', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-19 07:38:51'),
(798, 0, 'Golden Globes 2023', 'golden-globes-2023', '', '20', 'uploads/event/63c8f0a9b997d23-01-19-07-26-33.avif', 'Beverly Hilton Hotel', NULL, NULL, '', 'Beverly Hills, CA', 'US', '2023-01-11', '', '2023-01-11', '', 'The Golden Globe Awards are accolades bestowed by the Hollywood Foreign Press Association beginning in January 1944, recognizing excellence in both American and international film and television.', 'https://www.goldenglobes.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-19 07:26:33'),
(799, 0, 'Oscars Governors 2023', 'oscars-governors-2023', '', '20', 'uploads/event/63c78e073e82423-01-18-06-13-27.jpeg', 'Dolby Theatre at Ovation Hollywood', NULL, NULL, '', 'Hollywood, CA', 'US', '2023-03-12', '', '2023-03-12', '', 'The Governors Awards is an annual event celebrating awards conferred by the Academy\'s Board of Governors – the Irving G. Thalberg Memorial Award, the Jean Hersholt Humanitarian Award and the Honorary Award. Recipients are announced each summer and honored at a dinner gala in November.', 'https://www.oscars.org/governors', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 06:13:27'),
(800, 0, 'Grammys 2023', 'grammys-2023', '', '20', 'uploads/event/63c8f0f199e0f23-01-19-07-27-45.webp', 'Crypto.com Aren', NULL, NULL, '', 'Los Angeles, CA', 'US', '2023-02-05', '', '2023-02-05', '', 'The Grammy Award, or just Grammy, is an award presented by the Recording Academy to recognize \"Outstanding Achievement in the music industry\" of the United States. The trophy depicts a gilded gramophone. The Grammys are the first of the Big Three networks\' major music awards held annually.', 'https://www.grammy.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-19 07:27:45'),
(801, 0, 'BAFTA 2023', 'bafta-2023', '', '20', 'uploads/event/63c791de66b0a23-01-18-06-29-50.jpeg', 'London\'s Royal Festival Hall', NULL, NULL, '', 'Southbank Centre, Belvedere Rd, London SE1 8XX', 'UK', '2023-02-19', '', '2023-02-19', '', 'The first BAFTA Awards ceremony was held in 1949, and the ceremony was first broadcast on the BBC in 1956 with Vivien Leigh as the host.', 'https://www.bafta.org/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 06:29:50'),
(802, 0, 'Annie Awards 2023', 'annie-awards-2023', '', '20', 'uploads/event/63c792395c6c523-01-18-06-31-21.jpeg', 'UCLA ROYCE HALL.', NULL, NULL, '', 'Los Angeles, CA', 'US', '2023-02-25', '', '2023-02-22', '', 'The Annie Awards are accolades which the Los Angeles branch of the International Animated Film Association, ASIFA-Hollywood, has presented each year since 1972 to recognize excellence in animation shown in cinema and television.', 'https://annieawards.org/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 06:31:21'),
(803, 0, 'American Cinema Editors Eddie Awards ceremony', 'american-cinema-editors-eddie-awards-ceremony', '', '20', 'uploads/event/63c7927d8cb7c23-01-18-06-32-29.jpeg', 'UCLA ROYCE HALL.', NULL, NULL, '', 'Los Angeles, CA', 'US', '2023-03-05', '', '2023-03-05', '', 'Since 1951, American Cinema Editors has celebrated the best in television and feature film editing at the annual ACE Eddie Awards gala. More than a thousand of the entertainment industry\'s most accomplished editors, filmmakers and Hollywood elite attend the black-tie event held each year.', 'https://americancinemaeditors.org/eddie-awards/#:~:text=Since%201951%2C%20American%20Cinema%20Editors,tie%20event%20held%20each%20year.', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 06:32:29'),
(804, 0, 'Producers Guild of America Awards ceremony', 'producers-guild-of-america-awards-ceremony', '', '20', 'uploads/event/63c793007a9a123-01-18-06-34-40.webp', 'Fairmont Century Plaza Hotel', NULL, NULL, '', 'Los Angeles, CA', 'US', '2023-02-25', '', '2023-02-25', '', 'The 33rd Producers Guild of America Awards honors the best film and television producers.', 'https://producersguild.org/category/all-news/awards/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 06:34:40'),
(805, 0, 'Screen Actors Guild Awards ceremony', 'screen-actors-guild-awards-ceremony', '', '20', 'uploads/event/63c7935779b5123-01-18-06-36-07.jpeg', 'Shrine Exposition Center', NULL, NULL, '', 'Los Angeles, CA', 'US', '2023-02-26', '', '2023-02-28', '', 'Screen Actors Guild Awards are accolades given by the Screen Actors Guild-American Federation of Television and Radio Artists. The award was founded in 1952 to recognize outstanding performances in movie and prime time television.', 'https://www.sagawards.org/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 06:36:07'),
(806, 0, 'Art Directors Guild Awards ceremony', 'art-directors-guild-awards-ceremony', '', '20', 'uploads/event/63c793cf26f7823-01-18-06-38-07.jpeg', 'InterContinental Los Angeles Downtown', NULL, NULL, '', 'Los Angeles, CA', 'US', '2023-02-18', '', '2023-02-18', '', 'The ADG Excellence in Production Design Awards are awards presented annually by the Art Directors Guild (ADG) to recognize excellence in production design and art direction in the film and television industries. Honorees are presented with an award made by the New York firm Society Awards.', 'https://adg.org/awards/adg/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 1, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:04:00'),
(807, 0, 'Film Independent Spirit Awards ceremony', 'film-independent-spirit-awards-ceremony', '', '20', 'uploads/event/63c79bb4d110523-01-18-07-11-48.webp', 'In keeping with its Los Angeles roots, the Spirit Awards takes place each year in and around a beachfront tent in beautiful Santa Monica.', NULL, NULL, '', 'Santa Monica, CA', 'US', '2023-03-04', '', '2023-03-04', '', 'The Film Independent Spirit Awards is the premier awards event for the independent film and television community. Each year, the Spirit Awards brings together top talent from throughout the world of film and television.', 'https://www.filmindependent.org/spirit-awards/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:11:48'),
(808, 0, 'Costume Designers Guild Awards', 'costume-designers-guild-awards', '', '20', 'uploads/event/63c79bfaddb4b23-01-18-07-12-58.jpeg', 'Fairmont Century Plaza', NULL, NULL, '', 'Los Angeles, CA', 'US', '2023-02-27', '', '2023-02-27', '', 'The Costume Designers Guild, Local 892, is a union of professional costume designers, assistant costume designers, and illustrators working in film, television, commercials and other media. The CDG is not an employment agency, it is a labor union', 'https://www.costumedesignersguild.com/awards-current/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:12:58'),
(809, 0, 'Directors Guild of America Awards ceremony', 'directors-guild-of-america-awards-ceremony', '', '20', 'uploads/event/63c79c5f7bfb423-01-18-07-14-39.jpeg', 'Beverly Hilton Hotel', NULL, NULL, '', 'Beverly Hills, CA', 'US', '2023-02-18', '', '2023-02-18', '', 'The 74th Directors Guild of America Awards, honoring the outstanding directorial achievement in feature films, documentary, television and commercials of the year', 'https://www.dga.org/awards/annual.aspx', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:14:39'),
(810, 0, 'Writers Guild of America Awards ceremony', 'writers-guild-of-america-awards-ceremony', '', '20', 'uploads/event/63c79cb31c9a923-01-18-07-16-03.webp', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'TBA', 'US', '2023-03-05', '', '2023-03-05', '', 'The Writers Guild Awards honor outstanding writing in film, television, new media, news, radio, and promotional categories.', 'https://awards.wga.org/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:16:03'),
(811, 0, 'Frankfurt Fashion Week', 'frankfurt-fashion-week', '', '17', 'uploads/event/63c79d049b23e23-01-18-07-17-24.jpeg', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Frankfurt', 'GE', '2023-01-10', '', '2023-01-13', '', 'Frankfurt Fashion Week is the new home for a future-oriented fashion and lifestyle community. With its ecosystem of trade shows, conferences, runways, and events, the focus is on sustainability and digitalisation, bringing together decision-makers and forward-thinkers of the international fashion business.', 'https://frankfurt.fashion/en', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:17:24'),
(812, 0, 'Copenhagen Fashion Week', 'copenhagen-fashion-week', '', '17', 'uploads/event/63c79d44b91a723-01-18-07-18-28.jpg', 'Copenhagen City Hall', NULL, NULL, '', 'Copenhagen', 'DE', '2023-08-09', '', '2023-08-12', '', 'Copenhagen Fashion Week is the leading Nordic biannual fashion week held in January/February and August. Each season, esteemed industry leaders attend four days of showcases and events alongside the two trade shows CIFF and Revolver. Sustainability is the core focus area for Copenhagen Fashion Week.', 'https://copenhagenfashionweek.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:18:28'),
(813, 0, 'Madrid Fashion Week', 'madrid-fashion-week', '', '17', 'uploads/event/63c7a0b959d3723-01-18-07-33-13.png', 'Hall 14.1 at Feria de Madrid', NULL, NULL, '', 'Madrid', 'ESP', '2023-02-15', '', '2023-02-19', '', 'Mercedes-Benz Fashion Week Madrid is Spain\'s number one fashion show and the leading showcase for raising the profile of Spanish fashion around the world. It is organised by IFEMA MADRID and is held twice a year in Hall 14.1 at Feria de Madrid and in select venues around the city.', 'https://www.ifema.es/en/mbfw-madrid', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:33:13'),
(814, 0, 'New York Fashion Week Women\'s', 'new-york-fashion-week-womens', '', '17', 'uploads/event/63c7a207ed36d23-01-18-07-38-47.jpg', 'Skylight Clarkson Square', NULL, NULL, '', 'Manhattan, NY', 'US', '2023-02-14', '', '2023-02-14', '', 'New York Fashion Week (NYFW), held in February and September of each year, is a semi-annual series of events in Manhattan typically spanning 7–9 days when international fashion collections are shown to buyers, the press, and the general public.', 'https://nyfw.com/home/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:38:47'),
(815, 0, 'New York Fashion Week Bridal', 'new-york-fashion-week-bridal', '', '17', 'uploads/event/63c7a26a4e14e23-01-18-07-40-26.jpeg', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Manhattan, NY', 'US', '2023-10-11', '', '2023-10-14', '', 'New York Bridal Fashion Week is an industry event where designers and brands reveal their latest collections, twice a year in October and April, to brides, retail buyers, and the media.', 'https://fashionweekonline.com/bridal', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:40:26'),
(816, 0, 'New York Fashion Week Pre-Fall & Fall/Winter', 'new-york-fashion-week-pre-fall-fallwinter', '', '17', 'uploads/event/63c7a2f85dd7b23-01-18-07-42-48.jpeg', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Manhattan, NY', 'US', '', '', '', '', 'This New York Fashion Week for the Fall/Winter 2022 collections will be “almost normal” although hygiene protocols and vaccine certifications are the minimum requirements for attendants and organizers.', 'https://nyfw.com/home/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:42:48'),
(817, 0, 'London Fashion Week', 'london-fashion-week', '', '17', 'uploads/event/63c7a346d8bd423-01-18-07-44-06.webp', 'Hylo', NULL, NULL, '', 'London', 'UK', '2023-09-16', '', '2023-09-20', '', 'London Fashion Week is a clothing trade show that takes place in London twice a year, in February and September. Showcasing over 250 designers to a global audience of influential media and retailers, it is one of the \'Big Four\' fashion weeks, along with the New York, Milan and Paris.', 'https://londonfashionweek.co.uk/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:44:06'),
(818, 0, 'London Fashion Week Men\'s', 'london-fashion-week-mens', '', '17', 'uploads/event/63c7a39d5146023-01-18-07-45-33.jpg', 'Skylight Clarkson Square', NULL, NULL, '', 'Manhattan, NY', 'US', '2023-02-14', '', '2023-02-14', '', 'New York Fashion Week (NYFW), held in February and September of each year, is a semi-annual series of events in Manhattan typically spanning 7–9 days when international fashion collections are shown to buyers, the press, and the general public.', 'https://nyfw.com/home/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:45:33'),
(819, 0, 'Milan Fashion Week', 'milan-fashion-week', '', '17', 'uploads/event/63c7a3fbda09023-01-18-07-47-07.webp', 'Piazza del Duomo', NULL, NULL, '', 'Milan', 'IT', '2023-02-20', '', '2023-02-26', '', 'Milan Fashion Week is a clothing trade show held semi-annually in Milan, Italy. The autumn/winter event is held in February/March of each year, and the spring/summer event is held in September/October of each year. It is one of the most important worldwide.', 'https://fashionweekonline.com/milan', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:47:07');
INSERT INTO `events` (`id`, `category`, `title`, `slug`, `host`, `type`, `image`, `address`, `lat`, `lon`, `pin`, `suburb`, `state`, `start_date`, `start_time`, `end_date`, `end_time`, `description`, `link`, `contact_email`, `contact_phone`, `cost`, `recurring`, `color`, `status`, `subscription_status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(820, 0, 'Paris Fashion Week', 'paris-fashion-week', '', '17', 'uploads/event/63c7a47184e2523-01-18-07-49-05.jpeg', 'Carrousel du Louvre', NULL, NULL, '', 'Paris', 'FR', '2023-09-26', '', '2023-10-04', '', 'Paris Fashion Week is a series of designer presentations held semiannually in Paris, France with spring/summer and autumn/winter events held each year. Dates are determined by the French Fashion Federation. Paris Fashion Week is held at venues throughout the city.', 'https://fhcm.paris/en/paris-fashion-week-en/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:49:05'),
(821, 0, 'Paris Haute Couture Week', 'paris-haute-couture-week', '', '17', 'uploads/event/63c7a4cfa714c23-01-18-07-50-39.jpeg', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Paris', 'FR', '2023-09-26', '', '2023-10-04', '', 'Paris Fashion Week (French: Semaine de la mode de Paris) is a series of designer presentations held semiannually in Paris, France with spring/summer and autumn/winter events held each year. Dates are determined by the French Fashion Federation. Paris Fashion Week is held at venues throughout the city.', 'https://hautecouture.fhcm.paris/en/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:50:39'),
(822, 0, 'Shanghai Fashion Week', 'shanghai-fashion-week', '', '17', 'uploads/event/63c7a535c463423-01-18-07-52-21.jpeg', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Shanghai', 'CH', '2023-09-25', '', '2023-09-30', '', 'Shanghai Fashion Week is a fashion event held two times every year in Shanghai, each time lasting for seven days which is a part of Shanghai International Fashion Culture Festival which usually lasts for a month. The event first began in 2001.', 'https://www.shanghaifashionweek.com/page/shfw?language=en', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:52:21'),
(823, 0, 'Seoul Fashion Week', 'seoul-fashion-week', '', '17', 'uploads/event/63c7a5b176b2b23-01-18-07-54-25.jpeg', 'Dongdaemun Design Plaza', NULL, NULL, '', 'Seoul', 'South Korea', '2023-10-11', '', '2023-10-15', '', 'Seoul Fashion Week, South Korea\'s biggest biannual fashion show', 'https://www.seoulfashionweek.org/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:54:25'),
(824, 0, 'Winter World University Games', 'winter-world-university-games', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7a60221b4f23-01-18-07-55-46.jpeg', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Lake Placid', 'US', '2023-01-12', '', '2023-01-22', '', 'The 2023 FISU Winter World University Games, commonly known as Lake Placid 2023, is a collegiate multi-sport winter sports event scheduled to be held from January 12 to 22, 2023 in Lake Placid, New York, United States.', 'https://www.fisu.net/sport-events/fisu-world-university-games/winter-fisu-world-university-games', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:55:46'),
(825, 0, 'World Championships', 'world-championships', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7a66fc685023-01-18-07-57-35.jpeg', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'TBA', 'Poland / Sweden', '2023-01-12', '', '2023-01-29', '', 'A world championship is generally an international competition open to elite competitors from around the world, representing their nations, and winning such an event will be considered the highest or near highest achievement in the sport, game, or ability.', 'https://worldathletics.org/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:57:35'),
(826, 0, 'Men\'s Hockey World Cup', 'mens-hockey-world-cup', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7a6d36de0e23-01-18-07-59-15.jpeg', 'Kalinga Stadium', NULL, NULL, '', 'Bhubaneswar', 'IN', '2023-01-13', '', '2023-01-29', '', 'The Hockey World Cup is an international field hockey competition organized by the International Hockey Federation (FIH). The tournamewnt was founded in 1924 by Frenchman, Paul Leautey. It Since 1971, it is held every four years, between the Summer Olympics.', 'https://www.fih.hockey/events/world-cup', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 07:59:15'),
(827, 0, 'Winter X Games 27', 'winter-x-games-27', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7a74555da223-01-18-08-01-09.webp', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Aspen, Colorado', 'US', '2023-01-27', '', '2023-01-29', '', 'The X Games is a yearly sports event, controlled and managed by the American sports broadcasting channel, ESPN, which focuses on extreme sports. The first X Games were held in 1995 in Newport, Rhode Island. Held simultaneously to the X Games is the X Fest which is a sports and music', 'http://www.xgames.com/events/winter-x-games', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:01:09'),
(828, 0, 'Six Nations [Rugby]', 'six-nations-rugby', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7a78ed5edf23-01-18-08-02-22.jpeg', 'Principality Stadium', NULL, NULL, '', 'Cardiff, Wales', 'IR', '2023-02-04', '', '2023-03-18', '', 'The 6 nations championship is one of many events in the international Rugby Union calendar. It is an annual competition between six European sides: England, France, Ireland, Italy, Scotland and Wales. The Rugby Championship is a similar tournament in the Southern Hemisphere.', 'https://www.sixnationsrugby.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:02:22'),
(829, 0, 'Alpine World Ski Championships', 'alpine-world-ski-championships', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7a81ee1b2123-01-18-08-04-46.png', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Méribel', 'FR', '2023-02-06', '', '2023-02-19', '', 'The Alpine Skiing World Championships is the world\'s second largest winter sports event, only the Winter Olympic Games is larger.', 'https://www.fis-ski.com/en/alpine-skiing', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:04:46'),
(830, 0, 'ICC World T20 (women)', 'icc-world-t20-women', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7a86a4c1c323-01-18-08-06-02.jpeg', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'TBA', 'SA', '2023-02-10', '', '2023-02-26', '', 'The International Cricket Council (ICC) Women\'s T20 World Cup is the international championship of Twenty20 cricket for national women\'s teams. The ICC World T20 takes place approximately every two years.', 'https://womens.t20worldcup.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:06:02'),
(831, 0, 'FIS Nordic World Ski Championships', 'fis-nordic-world-ski-championships', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7a9066f24a23-01-18-08-08-38.jpeg', 'The Westin Resort, Costa Navarino', NULL, NULL, '', 'Pilos', 'GR', '2023-02-21', '', '2023-03-05', '', 'The FIS Nordic World Ski Championships is a biennial nordic skiing event organized by the International Ski Federation (FIS). The World Championships was started in 1925 for men and opened for women\'s participation in 1954.', 'https://www.planica2023.si/en', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:08:38'),
(832, 0, 'World Baseball Classic', 'world-baseball-classic', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7a9807115d23-01-18-08-10-40.jpeg', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'TBA', 'Japan, US, Taiwan', '2023-03-08', '', '2023-03-21', '', 'The World Baseball Classic is an international baseball tournament sanctioned from 2006 to 2013 by the International Baseball Federation and after 2013 by World Baseball Softball Confederation in partnership with Major League Baseball.', 'https://www.mlb.com/world-baseball-classic', '', '', 0.00, 'every-4-years', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:10:40'),
(833, 0, 'World Snooker Championship', 'world-snooker-championship', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7a9de4962023-01-18-08-12-14.png', 'Crucible Theatre', NULL, NULL, '', 'Sheffeld', 'ENG', '2023-04-15', '', '2023-05-01', '', 'The World Snooker Championship is a professional snooker tournament with prize money, ranking points and prestige. It\'s one of the Triple Crown snooker events besides the UK Championship and the Masters. The first official Snooker Championship was held in 1927 in Sheffield, England.', 'https://wst.tv/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:12:14'),
(834, 0, 'Grand National [Horse Racing]', 'grand-national-horse-racing', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7aa38eaf2123-01-18-08-13-44.webp', 'Aintree Racecourse', NULL, NULL, '', 'Liverpool', 'ENG', '2023-04-13', '', '2023-04-15', '', 'The Grand National is a National Hunt horse race held annually at Aintree Racecourse in Liverpool, England. First run in 1839, it is a handicap steeplechase over an official distance of about 4 miles and 2½ furlongs, with horses jumping 30 fences over two laps.', 'https://www.grandnational.org.uk/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:13:44'),
(835, 0, 'South-East Asian Games', 'south-east-asian-games', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7aa99be6b123-01-18-08-15-21.jpeg', 'Morodok Techo National Stadium', NULL, NULL, '', 'Phnom Penh', 'KH', '2023-05-05', '', '2023-05-17', '', 'The Southeast Asian Games, also known as the SEA Games, is a biennial multi-sport event involving participants from the current 11 countries of Southeast Asia', 'https://cambodia2023.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'every-2-years', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:15:21'),
(836, 0, 'Kentucky Derby [Horse Racing]', 'kentucky-derby-horse-racing', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7aae189e1423-01-18-08-16-33.jpeg', 'Churchill Downs', NULL, NULL, '', 'Kentucky', 'US', '2023-05-06', '', '2023-05-06', '', 'Kentucky Derby, the most prestigious American horse race, established in 1875 and run annually on the first Saturday in May at Churchill Downs racetrack, Louisville, Kentucky.', 'www.kentuckyderby.com', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:16:33'),
(837, 0, 'IIHF World Championship', 'iihf-world-championship', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7ab214490323-01-18-08-17-37.png', 'Nokia Arena', NULL, NULL, '', 'TBA', 'Finland - Latvia', '2023-12-26', '', '2023-01-05', '', 'The Ice Hockey World Championships are an annual international men\'s ice hockey tournament organized by the International Ice Hockey Federation. First officially held at the 1920 Summer Olympics, it is the sport\'s highest profile annual international tournament.', 'https://www.iihf.com/en/events/2023/wm', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:17:37'),
(838, 0, 'AFC Asian Cup [Football/Soccer]', 'afc-asian-cup-footballsoccer', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7aba10b9fd23-01-18-08-19-45.jpeg', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'TBA', 'China / South Korean', '2023-06-16', '', '2023-07-06', '', 'The AFC Asian Cup is the primary association football competition contested by the senior men\'s national teams of the members of the Asian Football Confederation, determining the continental champion of Asia. It is the second oldest continental football championship in the world after Copa América.', 'https://www.the-afc.com/en/home.html', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:19:45'),
(839, 0, 'NBA Finals', 'nba-finals', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7ac11a68d023-01-18-08-21-37.jpeg', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'TBA', 'US/CA', '2023-06-06', '', '2023-06-06', '', 'The NBA Finals is the annual championship series of the National Basketball Association. The Eastern and Western conference champions play a best-of-seven game series to determine the league champion.', 'https://www.nba.com/playoffs/2022/the-finals', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:21:37'),
(840, 0, 'World Aquatics Championships', 'world-aquatics-championships', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7ac73324db23-01-18-08-23-15.jpeg', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Fukuoka', 'JP', '2023-07-14', '', '2023-07-30', '', 'The FINA World Championships or World Aquatics Championships are the World Championships for aquatics sports: swimming, diving, high diving, open water swimming, artistic swimming, and water polo. They are run by FINA, and all swimming events are contested in a long course pool', 'https://www.fina.org/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:23:15'),
(841, 0, 'Women\'s World Cup', 'womens-world-cup', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7acdedd4bf23-01-18-08-25-02.webp', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'TBA', 'AU/NZ', '2023-07-10', '', '2023-08-20', '', 'The tournament replicates the format of the men\'s FIFA World Cup used between 1998 to 2022. The tournament also acts as the UEFA qualifiers for the 2024 Paris Olympic Games. The best-two UEFA teams from the World Cup will qualify (not including Olympic hosts France).', 'https://www.fifa.com/tournaments/womens/womensworldcup', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:25:02'),
(842, 0, 'World Police and Fire Games', 'world-police-and-fire-games', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7ad279f3e023-01-18-08-26-15.jpeg', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Winnipeg', 'CA', '2023-07-28', '', '2023-08-06', '', 'The World Police and Fire Games is a biennial athletic event, open to active and retired law enforcement and fire service personnel throughout the world. The WPFG Federation is an arm of the California Police Athletic Federation, an American non-profit organization.', 'https://wpfgrotterdam2022.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:26:15'),
(843, 0, 'Netball World Cup', 'netball-world-cup', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7ad9e37ec523-01-18-08-28-14.png', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Cape Town', 'SA', '2023-07-28', '', '2023-08-06', '', 'The Netball World Cup is a quadrennial international netball world championship organised by the World Netball, inaugurated in 1963.', 'https://netball.sport/events-and-results/netball-world-cup', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:28:14'),
(844, 0, 'Summer World University Games', 'summer-world-university-games', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7ae113171423-01-18-08-30-09.jpeg', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Chengdu', 'CH', '2023-07-28', '', '2023-08-08', '', 'The FISU World University Games are staged every two years in a different city. This celebration of international university sports and culture draws many thousands of student-athletes together to compete, making it among the world\'s largest and most prestigious multi-sport events.', 'https://www.fisu.net/sport-events/fisu-world-university-games/summer-fisu-world-university-games', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:30:09'),
(845, 0, 'UCI Cycling World Championships', 'uci-cycling-world-championships', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7aea10681a23-01-18-08-32-33.jpeg', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Glasgow, Scotland', 'UK', '2022-08-03', '', '2023-03-13', '', 'The 2022 UCI Road World Championships was the 95th edition of the UCI Road World Championships, the annual world championships for road bicycle racing. It was held between 18 and 25 September 2022 in Wollongong, New South Wales, Australia.', 'https://www.uci.org/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 08:32:33'),
(846, 0, 'World Beach Games', 'world-beach-games', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7ba65a551523-01-18-09-22-45.png', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Bali', 'ID', '2023-08-05', '', '2023-08-12', '', 'The ANOC World Beach Games, known simply as the World Beach Games, is an international multi-sport event organized by the Association of National Olympic Committees', 'https://www.anocolympic.org/anoc-world-beach-games/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:22:45'),
(847, 0, 'Sailing World Championships', 'sailing-world-championships', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7baad5a6d023-01-18-09-23-57.png', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'The Hauge', 'NE', '2023-08-10', '', '2023-08-20', '', 'The Sailing World Championships are the primary event in the Olympic qualification campaign and mirrors the Olympic sailing event format. All 10 Olympic events will be contested just one year out from Paris 2024.', 'https://www.sailing.org/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:23:57'),
(848, 0, 'IAAF World Championships', 'iaaf-world-championships', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7bb06b5d6c23-01-18-09-25-26.png', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Budapest', 'HU', '2023-08-19', '', '2023-08-27', '', 'The World Athletics Championships are a biennial athletics competition organized by World Athletics. Alongside the Olympic Games, they represent the highest level championships of senior international outdoor athletics competition for track and field athletics globally, including marathon running and race walking.', 'https://worldathletics.org/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:25:26'),
(849, 0, 'FIBA Basketball World Cup', 'fiba-basketball-world-cup', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7bb58b311123-01-18-09-26-48.png', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'TBA', 'ID, JP, PH', '2023-08-25', '', '2023-09-10', '', 'The FIBA Basketball World Cup, also known as the FIBA World Cup of Basketball or simply the FIBA World Cup, between 1950 and 2010 known as the FIBA World Championship, is an international basketball', 'https://www.fiba.basketball/basketballworldcup/2023', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:26:48'),
(850, 0, 'World Rowing Championships', 'world-rowing-championships', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7bb9a10f0823-01-18-09-27-54.png', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Belgrade, Serbia', 'EU', '2023-09-03', '', '2023-09-10', '', 'The World Rowing Championships is an international rowing regatta organized by FISA (the International Rowing Federation). It is a week-long event held at the end of the northern hemisphere summer and in non-Olympic years is the highlight of the international rowing calendar.', 'https://worldrowing.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:27:54'),
(851, 0, 'World Cup (men) [Rugby]', 'world-cup-men-rugby', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7bbee01d6623-01-18-09-29-18.png', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'TBA', 'FR', '2023-09-08', '', '2023-10-28', '', 'World Cup (men) [Rugby]', 'https://www.rugbyworldcup.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:29:18'),
(852, 0, 'Solheim Cup [Golf]', 'solheim-cup-golf', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7bc63af94c23-01-18-09-31-15.png', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Casares, Málaga, Andalusia', 'ESP', '2023-09-22', '', '2023-09-24', '', 'The Solheim Cup is a biennial golf tournament for professional women golfers contested by teams representing Europe and the United States. It is named after the Norwegian-American golf club manufacturer Karsten Solheim, who was a driving force behind its creation.', 'http://www.solheimcup.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:31:15'),
(853, 0, 'Ryder Cup [Golf]', 'ryder-cup-golf', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7bcaaabd1723-01-18-09-32-26.png', 'Marco Simone Golf and Country Club', NULL, NULL, '', 'Rome', 'Italy', '2023-09-29', '', '2023-10-01', '', 'The Ryder Cup is a biennial men\'s golf competition between teams from Europe and the United States. The competition is contested every two years with the venue alternating between courses in the United States and Europe. The Ryder Cup is named after the English businessman Samuel Ryder who donated the trophy.', 'https://www.rydercup.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:32:26'),
(854, 0, 'World Combat Games', 'world-combat-games', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7bcebd2a8123-01-18-09-33-31.png', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Riyadh', 'Saudi Arabia', '2023-10-05', '', '2023-10-14', '', 'The World Combat Games is an international multi-sport event featuring combat sports and martial arts. The games were founded by SportAccord (now known as the Global Association of International Sports Federations) as a way of bringing various martial arts and combative sports to an international audience.', 'https://gaisf.sport/world-combat-game/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:33:31'),
(855, 0, 'Pan American Games', 'pan-american-games', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7bd40953fc23-01-18-09-34-56.png', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Santiago', 'CH', '2023-10-20', '', '2023-11-05', '', 'The Pan American Games is a continental multi-sport event in the Americas featuring summer sports, in which thousands of athletes participate in a variety of competitions. The competition is held among athletes from nations of the Americas, every four years in the year before the Summer Olympic Games.', 'https://www.panamsports.org/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:34:56'),
(856, 0, 'Melbourne Cup [Horse Racing]', 'melbourne-cup-horse-racing', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7bd86a0b2a23-01-18-09-36-06.png', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Victoria', 'AU', '2023-11-07', '', '2023-11-01', '', 'The Melbourne Cup is Australia\'s most famous horse race held over a distance of 3200 metres at Flemington Racecourse in Melbourne.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:36:06'),
(857, 0, 'Pacific Games', 'pacific-games', '', '15', 'uploads/event/63c7bdd74952223-01-18-09-37-27.png', 'TBA', NULL, NULL, '', 'Honiara', 'Solomon Islands', '2023-11-19', '', '2023-12-01', '', 'The 2023 Pacific Games, officially known as the XVII Pacific Games, will be a continental multi-sport event for Oceania countries and territories that is scheduled to be held in Honiara, Solomon Islands between 19 November and 2 December 2023.', 'https://pacificgames.pngfacts.com/', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:37:27'),
(858, 0, 'Diwali Festival of Lights', 'diwali-festival-of-lights', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7beceed9e723-01-18-09-41-34.png', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'IN', '2023-10-24', '', '2023-10-24', '', 'Diwali is a festival of lights and is one of the major festivals celebrated by Hindus, Jains, and Sikhs. The festival usually lasts five days and is celebrated during the Hindu lunisolar month Kartika.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:41:34'),
(859, 0, 'Day of the Dead/el Día de los Muertos (Mexico)', 'day-of-the-deadel-dia-de-los-muertos-mexico', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7bf57243d023-01-18-09-43-51.png', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'MX', '2023-11-01', '', '2023-11-02', '', 'The Day of the Dead is a holiday traditionally celebrated on November 1 and 2, though other days, such as October 31 or November 6, may be included depending on the locality. It largely originated in Mexico, where it is mostly observed, but also in other places, especially by people of Mexican heritage elsewhere.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:43:51'),
(860, 0, 'Guy Fawkes Night (UK)', 'guy-fawkes-night-uk', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c02b890d123-01-18-09-47-23.png', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'UK', '2023-05-11', '', '2023-05-22', '', 'The British holiday, celebrated with fireworks and bonfires, commemorates the failed Gunpowder Plot of 1605. Observed in the United Kingdom every year on November 5, Guy Fawkes Day—also called Bonfire Night or Fireworks Night—commemorates a failed assassination attempt from over 400 years ago.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:47:23'),
(861, 0, 'Yi Peng Lantern Festival (Thailand)', 'yi-peng-lantern-festival-thailand', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c06005ae123-01-18-09-48-16.webp', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'TH', '2023-11-08', '', '2023-11-08', '', 'A week after the end of Buddhist Lent, Thailand celebrates Yi Peng Lantern Festival. It’s one of the biggest festivals in Thailand, when thousands gather to send floating lanterns into the sky. These are made from banana leaves and other plant matter, which are carried up by propane-generated flames before being released into the night sky.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, '', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:48:16'),
(862, 0, 'Remembrance Day (UK/Worldwide)', 'remembrance-day-ukworldwide', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c0c6ee84823-01-18-09-49-58.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'UK', '2023-11-11', '', '2023-11-11', '', 'Remembrance Day is a national holiday in the UK and other countries which were formerly part of the British Empire. It commemorates members of the armed forces who have lost their lives in war and also honours civilians who died during times of conflict. This commemorative day is usually signified by the wearing of poppies and the observation of two minutes silence. A special service is held at The Cenotaph monument in London, where the Queen lays a wreath to those who died.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, '', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:49:58'),
(863, 0, 'Thanksgiving (USA)', 'thanksgiving-usa', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c1096f81a23-01-18-09-51-05.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'US', '2023-11-24', '', '2023-11-24', '', 'Thanksgiving is a holiday celebrated on the 24th Thursday of November in the USA (and sometimes some other countries too). It’s a time to be with family, friends and loved ones; eat lots of amazing foods; give thanks for everything you have; and enjoy watching parades around Thanksgiving Day.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:51:05'),
(864, 0, 'St Andrew’s Day (Scotland)', 'st-andrews-day-scotland', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c1590662123-01-18-09-52-25.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'SCT', '2023-11-30', '', '2023-11-30', '', 'St Andrew’s Day is celebrated on 30th November in Scotland, but also by Scots around the world, to mark the historical figure of St Andrew. The religious observance of St Andrews Day takes place on the feast day of Saint Andrew — 30th of November.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, '', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:52:25'),
(865, 0, 'Nicholas Day (Christian)', 'nicholas-day-christian', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c1a60ecda23-01-18-09-53-42.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'NL', '2023-12-06', '', '2023-12-06', '', 'St Nicholas Day is a holiday celebrated on December 6th each year. The day commemorates Saint Nicholas – a Greek saint who was the inspiration for Santa Claus, Father Christmas and Kris Kringle – all famous names of festive figures in Western society!', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:53:42'),
(866, 0, 'Las Posadas (Mexico)', 'las-posadas-mexico', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c1ea1b03e23-01-18-09-54-50.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'MX', '2023-12-16', '', '2023-12-24', '', 'A very popular Christmas celebration in Mexico, Las Posadas takes place from 16th to 24th December. The origins of the festival have been traced back to a play performed by Spanish conquistadores and missionaries that tells the story of Mary and Joseph searching for a place to give birth to Jesus – an alternative celebration of the Christmas story.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:54:50'),
(867, 0, 'Hanukkah (Jewish)', 'hanukkah-jewish', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c23aec93623-01-18-09-56-10.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-12-16', '', '2023-12-26', '', 'A very popular Christmas celebration in Mexico, Las Posadas takes place from 16th to 24th December. The origins of the festival have been traced back to a play performed by Spanish conquistadores and missionaries that tells the story of Mary and Joseph searching for a place to give birth to Jesus – an alternative celebration of the Christmas story.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:56:10'),
(868, 0, 'Winter Solstice (Pagan/Secular)', 'winter-solstice-pagansecular', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c27a00e3323-01-18-09-57-14.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-12-21', '', '2023-12-21', '', 'The Winter Solstice is the shortest day of the year and usually occurs on either December 21st (most common) or 22nd (less common). It signals the end of winter and has been celebrated as a holiday for thousands of years. Different cultures celebrate this event in different ways – some see it as a time to reflect and appreciate the good things we have, others see it as a more mystical or spiritual celebration.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:57:14'),
(869, 0, 'Christmas Day (Christian/Secular)', 'christmas-day-christiansecular', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c2b40e87723-01-18-09-58-12.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-12-25', '', '2023-12-25', '', 'The day that marks the birth of Jesus Christ. Despite being a Christian celebration, Christmas is also widely celebrated by many non-Christians around the world as a secular holiday focused on family, friends and exchanging gifts.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:58:12'),
(870, 0, 'Boxing Day (UK/Former British Colonies)', 'boxing-day-ukformer-british-colonies', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c2f83eb6023-01-18-09-59-20.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', '(UK/Former British Colonies)', '2023-12-26', '', '2023-12-26', '', 'Boxing Day is an annual holiday held on 26th December each year. The name Boxing Day dates back to 19th Century, when it was common practice for employers to give their servants a gift known as a “Christmas box” on this day, and thus the day became associated with receiving gifts!', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 09:59:20'),
(871, 0, 'New Year’s Eve (Secular)', 'new-years-eve-secular', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c32a4ba1423-01-18-10-00-10.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-01-01', '', '2023-01-01', '', 'New Year’s Eve is celebrated around the world as a time to mark the end of one year and welcome in a new one. People often gather with friends, loved ones or workmates for celebrations including fireworks, dinner parties, special drinks and/or dancing. It’s also common for people to make resolutions for things they want to achieve or change during the next year.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, '', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:00:10'),
(872, 0, 'St Davids Day', 'st-davids-day', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c36b7ee1923-01-18-10-01-15.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'UK', '2023-03-01', '', '2023-03-01', '', 'Songkran is a three-day national holiday in Thailand, and it is one of the most important holidays to Thai people. It occurs around the 13th or 14th April each year, and marks the traditional New Year. During this holiday, many Buddhists will return to their home towns to pay respects at their family’s temples. The water festival also involves the spraying of water on others, which can be used to cool off in Thailand’s hot climate!', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:01:15'),
(873, 0, 'Shrove Tuesday', 'shrove-tuesday', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c3b60d11a23-01-18-10-02-30.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'UK', '2023-03-01', '', '2023-03-01', '', 'More popularly known as ‘Pancake Day’, Shrove Tuesday is the day before Ash Wednesday, which marks the start of Lent. This public holiday in England is typically celebrated with pancakes, traditionally made by mixing batter with eggs and slowly frying until crisp on each side.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:02:30'),
(874, 0, 'Hinamatsuri', 'hinamatsuri', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c3ee2ce7523-01-18-10-03-26.webp', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'JP', '2023-03-03', '', '2023-03-03', '', 'Hinamatsuri or ‘the doll festival’ is a very important event in Japan, where families with daughters will display their beautifully decorated dolls in the home. This is to wish for their daughters to grow up healthy and have many future opportunities. In celebration of this holiday it would be appropriate to serve traditional Japanese sweet adzuki-bean soup.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:03:26'),
(875, 0, 'International Women’s Day', 'international-womens-day', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c44f7e52023-01-18-10-05-03.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-03-08', '', '2023-03-08', '', 'International Women’s Day celebrates the economic, political and social achievements of women. It is held on the 8th of March every year to recognise the hard work of females all over the world, and signifies a call to action for accelerating gender parity.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:05:03'),
(876, 0, 'Holi Festival (Hinduism)', 'holi-festival-hinduism', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c4989161d23-01-18-10-06-16.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Countries with large Indian subcontinent popluations', '2023-03-18', '', '2023-03-18', '', 'Holi is a Hindu spring festival that marks the beginning of spring. Traditional celebrations include throwing coloured powders at friends and family, as well as enjoying deliciously sweet Indian treats. Holi is a fun and typical holiday, perfect for making your own Indian delicacies at home!', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:06:16'),
(877, 0, 'St Patrick’s Day', 'st-patricks-day', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c4ef1276823-01-18-10-07-43.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'IR', '2023-03-17', '', '2023-03-17', '', 'St Patrick’s Day is celebrated as a national holiday in Ireland on the 17th March, and is a celebration of all things Irish. Celebrations include parades, wearing green clothes and lots of festivity. Also known as ‘the luck o’ the Irish’, celebrating at a St Patrick’s Day party would be perfect for this occasion.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, '', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:07:43'),
(878, 0, 'Qingming Festival', 'qingming-festival', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c5319406b23-01-18-10-08-49.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'CH', '2023-04-05', '', '2023-04-05', '', 'The Qingming Festival is a traditional Chinese holiday that falls on the fifth of April, and it is also known as Tomb Sweeping Day. It is a time to remember those who have passed away, by honouring them with visits to their graves and leaving offerings. This celebration is observed by many Chinese-speaking countries.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:08:49'),
(879, 0, 'Songkran', 'songkran', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c56e2282f23-01-18-10-09-50.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'TH', '2023-04-13', '', '2023-04-15', '', 'Songkran is a three-day national holiday in Thailand, and it is one of the most important holidays to Thai people. It occurs around the 13th or 14th April each year, and marks the traditional New Year. During this holiday, many Buddhists will return to their home towns to pay respects at their family’s temples. The water festival also involves the spraying of water on others, which can be used to cool off in Thailand’s hot climate!', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:09:50'),
(880, 0, 'Good Friday (Christian)', 'good-friday-christian', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c5aac91fe23-01-18-10-10-50.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-04-07', '', '2023-04-07', '', 'Good Friday is a Christian holiday that falls on the 15th of April every year. In the UK, it is a public bank holiday, and many people will go to church or visit ancestral graves before going out for lunch with family members, or spending the rest of the day relaxing with family. Good Friday traditionally represents the day that Jesus was crucified, and is celebrated by Christians as being the day he died for their sins.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, '', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:10:50'),
(881, 0, 'Easter Sunday (Christian)', 'easter-sunday-christian', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c5ee9d9ea23-01-18-10-11-58.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-04-09', '', '2023-04-09', '', 'Easter Sunday is observed by Christians as the day Jesus rose again. This date varies depending on the lunar cycle as Easter is a moveable date. It is always celebrated on a Sunday after the Spring Equinox, and in 2022, it falls on 17th April. Similar to Good Friday, Easter Sunday is a public bank holiday; during this time it is customary for children to share Easter eggs, chocolate and sweets with their family members while spending time together, or taking part in an Easter egg hunt!', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, '', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:11:58'),
(882, 0, 'Earth Day', 'earth-day', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c634a9a1923-01-18-10-13-08.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-04-22', '', '2023-04-22', '', 'Earth Day is a day of global celebration of the Earth, and it is observed all over the world. It is held on April 22nd every year, to raise awareness towards environmental issues, and for people to do their part in protecting our planet. Many charities organise events to take place during this time, including tree planting or beach clean-ups.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:13:08'),
(883, 0, 'St George’s Day (Europe)', 'st-georges-day-europe', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c68e8689123-01-18-10-14-38.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'EU', '2023-04-23', '', '2023-04-23', '', 'St George’s Day is mainly celebrated in the UK, but it is also a public holiday in other European countries such as Austria, Cyprus, Greece and Bulgaria. It falls on the 23rd of April every year. This day is commemorated to honour St George who was honoured by Christianity for being brave and courageous.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:14:38'),
(884, 0, 'Mayday (Europe)', 'mayday-europe', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c6d60316b23-01-18-10-15-50.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'EU', '2023-04-30', '', '2023-04-30', '', 'MAYDAY Dortmund is one of the most iconic dance music events on the European continent. Its legacy long outstrips their partying peers, considering that MAYDAY have been throwing the most extravagant, hedonistic raves for nearly thirty years since it\'s birth in 1991.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:15:50'),
(885, 0, 'Vappu (Finland)', 'vappu-finland', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c725f30b623-01-18-10-17-09.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'FN', '2023-05-01', '', '2023-05-01', '', 'Vappu is a huge public carnival that happens annually around May 1st. It is dedicated to the Finnish culture and traditions, and mainly involves students and other young people, who attend huge gatherings in different parts of the country. There are also many concerts and parties held to celebrate this time, and festivities such as wearing colourful clothes or ribbons on your clothing are customary!', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:17:09'),
(886, 0, 'Star Wars Day', 'star-wars-day', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c7867238323-01-18-10-18-46.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'CA', '2023-05-04', '', '2023-05-04', '', 'Star Wars Day is a humourous tradition, celebrated to mark the events of the Star Wars movie saga. On this day, fans are encouraged to celebrate by watching their favourite movies again or try dressing up as one of the characters! For many people worldwide, it is also customary to wish each other “may the 4th be with you!”, the joke behind the day itself.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:18:46'),
(887, 0, 'Cinco de Mayo (Mexico)', 'cinco-de-mayo-mexico', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c7bfe6df223-01-18-10-19-43.webp', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'MX', '2023-05-05', '', '2023-05-05', '', 'Cinco de Mayo is a national holiday in Mexico, held to commemorate the Mexican victory at the Battle of Puebla, 1862. On this day every year, Mexicans honour their country’s military by organising parades or festivals with food stalls selling traditional Mexican dishes.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:19:43'),
(888, 0, 'Vesak/Buddha Day (Buddhism)', 'vesakbuddha-day-buddhism', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c8269932c23-01-18-10-21-26.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Theravada countries following the Buddhist calendar, i', '2023-05-05', '', '2023-05-05', '', 'Vesak, also known as Buddha day, is an important Buddhist holiday that marks the birth, enlightenment and death of Gautama Buddha. The date changes every year depending on the lunar cycle, but it is always celebrated in the beginning of May. Buddha Day celebrations often include meditation and prayer, as well as many cultural activities such as dancing, art workshops and processions.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:21:26'),
(889, 0, 'Pride Month', 'pride-month', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c86d236ee23-01-18-10-22-37.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-01-06', '', '2023-01-30', '', 'The purpose of Pride Month is to acknowledge the struggles that the LGBT+ community has had to face in order to achieve equal rights, and also celebrate diversity and difference. This has been celebrated for over 50 years now, with the first ever pride parade taking place in 1970. Now, Pride Month is held in June every year, and there are many different events taking place across the world, many of which include parades or parties.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:22:37'),
(890, 0, 'Dragon Boat Festival (China)', 'dragon-boat-festival-china', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c8bcd1b0c23-01-18-10-23-56.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'CH', '2023-06-22', '', '2023-06-22', '', 'The Dragon Boat festival is one of the oldest traditional Chinese festivals and has a history of over 2000 years. The festival traditionally evolved from the practice of revering the river dragon, and involves a variety of ceremonies and activities. It takes place in June every year, with celebrations including dragon boat races, where they paddle and race their boats and hold handmade dragons above them!', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:23:56'),
(891, 0, 'Juneteenth (USA)', 'juneteenth-usa', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c904783cd23-01-18-10-25-08.webp', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'US', '2023-06-19', '', '2023-06-19', '', 'Juneteenth marks the celebration of black freedom in America. The tradition began as a time to rejoice and mark the end of slavery, but has since evolved into a day that highlights African American culture and achievements.The holiday is usually celebrated on June 19th every year, and is usually marked by several community events, street celebrations, picnics and family gatherings.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:25:08'),
(892, 0, 'World Refugee Day (Worldwide)', 'world-refugee-day-worldwide', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c99e2a87023-01-18-10-27-42.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-06-20', '', '2023-06-20', '', 'Organised by the United Nations, World Refugee Day is an annual event held on 20th June every year which gives the opportunity to raise awareness of the situations faced by refugees all around the world. Welcoming refugees can play a big role in helping them make a home for themselves in their new country, making this an important cultural event for your calendar this year.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:27:42'),
(893, 0, 'Canada Day (Canada)', 'canada-day-canada', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7c9e9dfc5b23-01-18-10-28-57.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'CA', '2023-07-01', '', '2023-07-01', '', 'Canada Day is marks the anniversary of the enactment of the Constitution Act, 1867. This act united three colonies into one single country – Canada – within the British Empire. This day has significant meaning to Canadians, as it is celebrated with parades, festivals and family events all across the country!', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:28:57'),
(894, 0, 'Independence Day (USA)', 'independence-day-usa', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7ca3c2203123-01-18-10-30-20.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'US', '2023-07-04', '', '2023-07-04', '', 'Independence Day is a federal holiday celebrated on the Fourth of July every year. This day celebrates the adoption of the Declaration of Independence and it’s important for Americans as it symbolises their independence from Great Britain.This day always involves fireworks, parades and family events, and should definitely be marked on your calendar this year!', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:30:26'),
(895, 0, 'Eid al Adha (Islamic)', 'eid-al-adha-islamic', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7cdc0ef6de23-01-18-10-45-20.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-06-29', '', '2023-06-29', '', 'Eid is an Islamic religious holiday, marking the end of the month of Ramadan. Celebrations for Eid include prayer, gift giving and family time, and both Eid al Adha and Eid al Fitr are public holidays in many countries including Egypt, Somalia, Turkey and Saudi Arabia.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 10:45:33'),
(896, 0, 'Naadam Festival (Mongolia)', 'naadam-festival-mongolia', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7d2a4916cc23-01-18-11-06-12.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Mongolia', '2023-07-11', '', '2023-07-15', '', 'The Naadam Festival in Mongolia is a significant event that takes place on the 11th of July every year. It usually includes three games: archery, horse riding and Mongolian wrestling. Mongolians consider these sports to be very important as they celebrate the history of the country’s nomadic lifestyle and culture. The Naadam Festival is accompanied by lots of music, food, drink and dancing!', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 11:06:12'),
(897, 0, 'Bastille Day (France)', 'bastille-day-france', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7d2fc8646d23-01-18-11-07-40.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'FR', '2023-07-14', '', '2023-07-14', '', 'Bastille Day is a French holiday which celebrates the storming of the Bastille, a famous prison in France. It was on this day in 1789 that prisoners were freed from the prison and it signalled the start of The French Revolution, marking an important event in their history. Bastille Day is often marked by fireworks, parades, dancing and singing in the streets!', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 11:07:40'),
(898, 0, 'Raksha Bandhan (Hindu)', 'raksha-bandhan-hindu', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7d35365da523-01-18-11-09-07.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'IN', '2023-08-30', '', '2023-08-30', '', 'Raksha Bandhan is a Hindu festival of brotherly love, which encourages the tying of Rakhi, a thread worn around the wrist or neck by Hindus as a symbol of love. Women will often tie this thread onto their brothers’ wrist as an act of protection and to signify the brother-sister bond. This festival is celebrated all across India and in Hindu communities worldwide.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 11:09:07'),
(899, 0, 'Obon (Japanese Buddhist)', 'obon-japanese-buddhist', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7d3aa28ca223-01-18-11-10-34.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'JP', '2023-08-13', '', '2023-08-13', '', 'Obon is a three day Buddhist festival that takes place every year. It honors the spirits of ancestors and it is believed that during this time, the souls of those who have died will visit their living relatives for a short time. It is an important part of Japanese culture and is celebrated with Bon Odori, or Bon Festival dance. This dance is often performed in public squares around the world, with participants wearing colourful kimono and dancing to traditional Japanese music. Obon is accompanied by many street stalls selling delicious festival food, so be sure to try some on this year’s Obon!', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 11:10:34'),
(900, 0, 'Krishna Janmashtami (Hindu)', 'krishna-janmashtami-hindu', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7d3ef636c523-01-18-11-11-43.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Northern India', '2023-08-18', '', '2023-08-18', '', 'Krishna Janmashtami is a celebration of the birth of Lord Krishna, one of the most important deities in Hinduism. It is celebrated with processions and gatherings in temples across the country, often involving singing and dancing.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 11:11:43'),
(901, 0, 'La Tomatina (Spain)', 'la-tomatina-spain', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7d43a1853523-01-18-11-12-58.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'ESP', '2023-08-31', '', '2023-08-31', '', 'La Tomatina is a large tomato-throwing festival in Spain. It’s held on the last Wednesday of August every year, and participants throw tomatoes at one another in the streets before cleaning up later in the day with refreshing water. This festival is highly popular with tourists, so why not go and join in yourself this year? Our Spanish Language Course can help you prepare for your trip!', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 11:12:58');
INSERT INTO `events` (`id`, `category`, `title`, `slug`, `host`, `type`, `image`, `address`, `lat`, `lon`, `pin`, `suburb`, `state`, `start_date`, `start_time`, `end_date`, `end_time`, `description`, `link`, `contact_email`, `contact_phone`, `cost`, `recurring`, `color`, `status`, `subscription_status`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(902, 0, 'Labour Day (USA/Canada)', 'labour-day-usacanada', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7d491a4cc323-01-18-11-14-25.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'CA', '2023-09-04', '', '2023-09-04', '', 'Labor Day is celebrated in the USA and Canada, marking the end of summer and the start of a new school year. Labor Day is observed on the first Monday of September every year, and celebrates the American labor movement and the contributions and achievements of American workers.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 11:14:25'),
(903, 0, 'Mid-Autumn Moon Festival (East/South East Asia)', 'mid-autumn-moon-festival-eastsouth-east-asia', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7d4dc6254e23-01-18-11-15-40.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'CH', '2023-09-10', '', '2023-09-10', '', 'The Mid-Autumn Moon Festival is a three day festival which is held in East and South East Asia. It takes place on the 15th day of the 8th month of the Chinese lunar calendar and celebrates the mid-autumn full moon and harvest, accompanied by family gatherings and delicious food!', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 11:15:40'),
(904, 0, 'International Day of Peace', 'international-day-of-peace', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c8f1b91443d23-01-19-07-31-05.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-09-21', '', '2023-09-21', '', 'The International Day of Peace is a United Nations observance and has been celebrated since 1982. It marks the opening for the annual debate of the General Assembly on disarmament and international security, as well as recognising and strengthening the ideals of peace within individuals, communities and societies across the globe.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-19 07:31:05'),
(905, 0, 'Rosh Hashana (Jewish)', 'rosh-hashana-jewish', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7d614101f323-01-18-11-20-52.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-09-15', '', '2023-09-17', '', 'Rosh Hashana is the first of the Jewish High Holy Days and marks the new year on the Hebrew calendar. This festival has many traditions including special foods, blowing shofar or ram’s horn and special services in synagogues.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 11:20:52'),
(906, 0, 'World Maritime Day', 'world-maritime-day', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7ec08dd0a223-01-18-12-54-32.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-09-28', '', '2023-09-28', '', 'The International Maritime Organisation (IMO) has been celebrating World Maritime Day since 1948. The day is used to celebrate and promote the safe, secure and efficient use of our oceans and seas for trade and transport as how we rely on them today.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 12:54:32'),
(907, 0, 'World Space Week', 'world-space-week', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7ec471cfb123-01-18-12-55-35.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-10-04', '', '2023-10-10', '', 'World Space Week is celebrated every October since 1999, and takes place between the 4th and 10th of the month. It’s a time to reflect on the benefits of space-based technologies for humankind, but also to look at our direct connection with space exploration through events like concerts, lectures and exhibitions.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, '', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 12:55:35'),
(908, 0, 'Yom Kippur (Jewish)', 'yom-kippur-jewish', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7ec7f5134823-01-18-12-56-31.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-09-24', '', '2023-09-25', '', 'Yom Kippur is the holiest day of the year for the Jewish people, and is a time for reflection on past actions. For 25 hours from sundown on the 9th of October, Jewish people fast and spend time in synagogue reflecting. This religious holy day lasts until sundown the following day. If you have any questions about this closer to the time, feel free to ask a Jewish colleague or friend!', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 12:56:31'),
(909, 0, 'World Mental Health Day', 'world-mental-health-day', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7ecb1e82df23-01-18-12-57-21.png', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-10-10', '', '2023-10-10', '', 'World Mental Health Day is a World Health Organisation (WHO) international day, held on 10 October each year. It aims to encourage open discussion of mental health issues and remove the stigma associated with mental illness, whilst also encouraging people to consider how physical health conditions have an impact on our mental wellbeing.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, '', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 12:57:21'),
(910, 0, 'Diwali Festival of Lights (Hindu)', 'diwali-festival-of-lights-hindu', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7ecdc65c3b23-01-18-12-58-04.webp', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-11-12', '', '2023-11-12', '', 'Diwali is one of the most important festivals celebrated by Hindus, Sikhs and Jains throughout the world. It signifies the triumph of good over evil, light over dark and knowledge over ignorance. As the Festival of Lights, celebrations often include lighting small oil lamps on the floor in front of statues of deities, dancing, eating and sharing gifts with friends and family.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 12:58:04'),
(911, 0, 'Sharad Navratri (Hinduism)', 'sharad-navratri-hinduism', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c7ed20bd7d423-01-18-12-59-12.webp', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-10-26', '', '2023-10-26', '', 'Sharad Navratri is one of the biggest and most important festivals celebrated in India. It’s also known as Navaratri or ‘nine nights’, beginning near the autumn equinox and culminating nine days later in Dussehra, commemorating the Hindu Goddess Durga defeating demon Mahishasura.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 12:59:12'),
(912, 0, 'Armageddon Time', 'armageddon-time', '', '20', 'uploads/event/63c7ed521a93d23-01-18-01-00-02.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2022-11-11', '', '2022-11-11', '', 'n/a', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, '', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-18 13:00:02'),
