(965, 0, 'Labour Day [AU]', 'labour-day-au', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c8e265b376723-01-19-06-25-41.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'AU', '2023-05-16', '', '2023-05-16', '', 'Labour Day, also known as Eight Hours Day in Tasmania and May Day in the Northern Territory, commemorates the granting of the eight-hour working day for Australians. It also recognizes workers’ contributions towards the nation’s economy. It is an annual public holiday and its date varies across the states and territories.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-19 06:25:41'),
