(984, 0, 'International Dog Day', 'international-dog-day', '', '18', 'uploads/event/63c8e6fd4130f23-01-19-06-45-17.jpeg', 'n/a', NULL, NULL, '', 'n/a', 'Worldwide', '2023-08-26', '', '2023-08-26', '', 'All purebred and mixed breed dogs are celebrated on National Dog Day. One of the goals of the holiday is for people to recognize how many dogs need to get rescued every year. The holiday also acknowledges working and family dogs that work every day to bring us comfort and save lives.', 'n/a', '', '', 0.00, 'annual', NULL, 1, 7, '2023-01-17 13:06:55', '2023-01-19 06:45:17'),
