(8, 'Copywriter', 'copywriter', NULL, 3, 'Full time', 'We are looking for a content writer to work with our design and digital marketing company to assist with the following activities.', '<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; line-height: 1.43; color: rgb(45, 45, 45);\">We would love to get to know you, so please include a&nbsp;<b>cover letter</b>&nbsp;introducing yourself.</p><ul style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; line-height: 1.43; color: rgb(45, 45, 45);\"><li>Must provide writing samples</li><li>Produce original content for use in demand generation and sales including blogs, emails, ad copy, video copy, social media posts, and sales collateral (one-pagers, landing pages, infographics, webinars, etc.)</li><li>Develop concepts and copy for numerous consumer-facing multichannel campaigns</li><li>Read and review creative briefs, attend kickoff meetings, and actively engage and ask questions at project inception</li><li>Generate multiple concepts and copy directions based on insights from creative briefs</li><li>Work with the Art Directors, Brand Strategists, and other marketing specialists to create breakthrough campaigns and tactical executions</li><li>Work in a variety of marketing channels; from traditional to non-traditional to see what drives results</li><li>Assisting with setting up, tracking, and iterating creative and out-of-the-box multi-channel marketing campaigns.</li><li>Proactively identifying new and innovative initiatives to support our brand and messaging</li><li>Highly flexible role - you enjoy working on writing email copy one week, direct mail programs the next, and brainstorming new campaigns and tactics the week after</li></ul>', NULL, '1315 Princes Hwy', 2000, 'liverpool', 'New south wales', 'Australia', 'python||laravel', '', '2 years', NULL, '', '', '1000', 'Vintage Cellars', 'lorem ipsum', '2022-12-10', '2023-01-21', '', 1, 0, 0, '2022-12-02', '2022-12-02', 'Highly flexible role - you enjoy working on writing email copy one week, direct mail programs the next, and brainstorming new campaigns and tactics the week after||Assisting with setting up, tracking, and iterating creative and out-of-the-box multi-channel marketing campaigns.', '1 month', 'Flexible schedule||Work from home', '', '', 'https://www.lipsum.com', '');

