(4, 7, 'Martha Smith', 'World Politics Editor', 'aerdvger', 'Martha Smith', 'uploads/testimonial/63987bf76c37a22-12-13-01-19-51.jpeg', 'Julian is one of those writers who are able to distinguish their own voice throughout any piece of work, without losing the soul of the publication itself. He\'s able to pick up on some of the finer nuances of the political climate and express them in word', '', '', '2022-12-13 13:19:51', '2022-12-13 13:20:38');

